video.title: Queer Eye
video.synopsis: Grab some tissues! An all-new "Fab Five" serve up hip tips, emotionally charged makeovers and heartfelt reveals that bring out all the feels.

episodes.synopsis: The Fab Five help a timid gay pastor who came out in his 30s update his look and find the confidence to lead his congregation into the future.
episodes.title: Preaching Out Loud

episodes.synopsis: To get her stalled mobile dog grooming business back in gear, a scrappy entrepreneur must polish her brand — and add some swag to her own wag.
episodes.title: Groomer Has It

episodes.synopsis: A divorced dad who hides behind baggy clothes and crusty hair gel gets a dazzling makeover — and learns to dance — for his daughter's wedding day.
episodes.title: Father of the Bride

episodes.synopsis: He's a humble hero who's survived homelessness — and helped young writers in his community hone their voices. Now he's ready for his next chapter.
episodes.title: The North Philadelphia Story

episodes.synopsis: A passionate Gen Z activist is so focused on saving the planet that she forgets to schedule self-care. Can the Fab Five help her find balance?
episodes.title: The Anxious Activist

episodes.synopsis: On a detour to the Jersey Shore, the Fab Five meet a single DJ who's ready to remaster his life and stop comparing himself to his married siblings.
episodes.title: DJ's on Repeat

episodes.synopsis: A devoted supermom worried about her husband's health slows down to make time for herself as she prepares to send her youngest off to college.
episodes.title: Silver Lining Sweeney

episodes.synopsis: A week off with the Fab Five reminds a tireless fishmonger that his dreams of opening up a restaurant don't have to come between him and his family.
episodes.title: Father Knows Fish

episodes.synopsis: A working mom yearns to balance her home life and career as a pediatrician, but her look screams "medical student." Time for some style tips stat.
episodes.title: Paging Dr. Yi

episodes.synopsis: His life and his business have seen better days. But this lovable West Philly fitness trainer is finally motivated to whip things back into shape.
episodes.title: Body Rock or Bust

episodes.synopsis: Jonathan returns to his hometown to make over his high school music teacher, a selfless educator whose fiery red mullet hasn't changed in 30 years.
episodes.title: Without Further Ado

episodes.synopsis: A former bad boy who turned his life around after becoming paralyzed gets a wheelchair-accessible home and a new image to match his positive outlook.
episodes.title: Disabled but Not Really

episodes.synopsis: His 10-year-old daughter calls him a "man child." But can this larger-than-life single dad grow up and become the adult she needs him to be?
episodes.title: Stoner Skates By

episodes.synopsis: A demanding drill-team leader who’s set in her ways learns to shed her tough skin, soften her style -- and open up to her two grown daughters.
episodes.title: How Wanda Got Her Groove Back

episodes.synopsis: The Fab Five help a kind but lonely bachelor find unconditional love and get his dusty home ready for visitors, the first guests he's had in years.
episodes.title: On Golden Kenny

episodes.synopsis: A proud Chicana woman and arts advocate trades her dated locks for a polished look that gives her the confidence to talk publicly about her passions.
episodes.title: A Tale of Two Cultures

episodes.synopsis: A scruffy ex-soldier who builds houses for homeless veterans spruces up to reconnect with his wife and finds unexpected strength in vulnerability.
episodes.title: Soldier Returns Home

episodes.synopsis: A recently divorced farmer who's weathered hard times makes room for self-care and turns his barn into a chic farm-to-table dining space.
episodes.title: Farm to Able

episodes.synopsis: She can hunt, fish and grow her own food. But this self-sufficient woman needs help when it comes to crafting a look that’s both womanly and powerful.
episodes.title: From Hunter to Huntee

episodes.synopsis: The Fab Five go back to camp to help a scraggly outdoorsman put down roots and create a cool home for his teenage son.
episodes.title: Lost Boy

episodes.synopsis: They've built a business on slow-cooked barbecue -- and a secret sauce. Now these hardworking sisters are finally getting the break they deserve.
episodes.title: Jones Bar-B-Q

episodes.synopsis: With his wedding just days away, a self-deprecating groom must learn to love himself before he's ready to walk down the aisle.
episodes.title: When Robert Met Jamie

episodes.synopsis: A young lesbian struggling with her identity opens her heart to let people in, only to discover she's much stronger than she realized.
episodes.title: Black Girl Magic

episodes.synopsis: A still-grieving single father whose wife died of cancer vows to honor her memory by moving forward with their two young sons.
episodes.title: Elrod & Sons

episodes.synopsis: A sweet but shy gamer who's spent his life in front of a screen finds the courage to make new friends and find his tribe.
episodes.title: Sloth to Slay

episodes.synopsis: Asking for help is hard for this serial procrastinator. But with his house in disarray -- and a baby on the way -- it's time to step up.
episodes.title: Baby on Board

episodes.synopsis: A devoutly religious woman with a gay son and a giving heart gets a new look -- and a makeover for her church's new community center.
episodes.title: God Bless Gay

episodes.synopsis: A scraggly film buff reboots his life -- and his nonexistent grooming habits -- to give his girlfriend an award-worthy marriage proposal.
episodes.title: A Decent Proposal

episodes.synopsis: A married bartender and father of two who lives like a messy bachelor needs to pull it together in time for a parent-teacher mixer.
episodes.title: Unleash the Sexy Beast

episodes.synopsis: A free-spirited Mr. Fix-It who lives for Burning Man makes big changes to prepare for a cross-country move. But his best friend doesn't want him to go.
episodes.title: The Handyman Can

episodes.synopsis: The Fab Five help a trans man who's recovering from top surgery throw a party to thank his friends who've shown unconditional love and support.
episodes.title: Sky's the Limit

episodes.synopsis: A jobless couch potato who can't stop lying is forced to start fresh and tell his mom the truth: that he didn't actually graduate from college.
episodes.title: Big Little Lies

episodes.synopsis: He's a singer, songwriter and pianist who's only 18. But he dresses like he's decades older, thanks to a godmother who's done everything for him.
episodes.title: Bedazzled

episodes.synopsis: The "hipster mayor" of a small town has really big plans. But first he needs to upgrade his look so that others will start taking him seriously.
episodes.title: Make Ted Great Again

episodes.synopsis: A lonely dump-truck driver with a big ol' heart goes from "ugly" to unbelievable and learns how to reverse years of bad habits.
episodes.title: You Can't Fix Ugly

episodes.synopsis: He's drowning in dog hair and prefers to keep his friends at a distance. But this self-deprecating app builder is finally ready to let folks in.
episodes.title: Saving Sasquatch

episodes.synopsis: A NASCAR enthusiast and former Marine known for his wild parties and crazy costumes makes an effort to dress up and connect with his family.
episodes.title: Dega Don't

episodes.synopsis: An emotional makeover helps the self-proclaimed "Straightest Gay Guy in Atlanta" come out to his stepmother and make peace with his past.
episodes.title: To Gay or Not Too Gay

episodes.synopsis: The Fab Five pull off a miracle with a devoutly Christian father of six by redesigning his tiny home and giving his bride the reception she never had.
episodes.title: Camp Rules

episodes.synopsis: After inheriting his grandmother's home -- and her dated decor -- a young entrepreneur digs his way out of a time warp to find his own style.
episodes.title: The Renaissance of Remington

episodes.synopsis: A subdued stand-up comic who lacks self-confidence after a major weight loss is swimming in big, baggy clothes. And he still lives with his parents.
episodes.title: Below Average Joe

episodes.synopsis: A selfless firefighter jumps at the chance to revamp his image and give his fire station a sleek, new look just in time for a community fundraiser.
episodes.title: Hose Before Bros
